{{!
  Block AI Assistant - Main Template
  Handles user interaction, history lookup cache check, SSE streaming, response rendering.
  
  Key flow:
  1. User clicks send
  2. sendMessage() called (now async)
  3. lookupHistory() queries DB for existing response
  4. If hit: render cached response + "Fetched from history" notice, return (no API call, no DB insert)
  5. If miss: create history row, start SSE stream, update row when complete
}}


